### Health
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/health

### Readiness
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/health/readiness

### Submit demo text
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/documents/text
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "BE13 Demo Paper",
  "text": "Demo AI Education Paper\n\nAbstract\nAI writing assistants may reduce drafting time for students (Smith, 2023).\n\nIntroduction\nPrior research suggests that AI writing assistants can improve drafting speed (Smith, 2023). However, broad claims about learning outcomes need careful review (Lee, 2022).\n\nReferences\nSmith, J. (2023). AI Writing Assistants and Drafting Speed. Journal of AI Education. https://doi.org/10.1234/demo.ai.2023\nLee, A. (2022). Learning Outcomes Without DOI. Academic Press."
}

### Extract references
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/documents/{{document_id}}/extract-references

### Extract claims
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/documents/{{document_id}}/extract-claims
Content-Type: application/json

{"mode":"citation_linked_only"}

### Prepare evidence
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/documents/{{document_id}}/prepare-evidence

### Run verification pipeline
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/documents/{{document_id}}/pipeline-runs
Content-Type: application/json

{"mode":"FULL_VERIFICATION","use_cache":true,"use_rag":true,"use_genai_safety_review":true,"generate_report":false}

### Generate report
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/documents/{{document_id}}/reports
Content-Type: application/json

{"format":"HTML","include_evidence_chunks":true,"include_human_review_items":true,"include_limitations":true}
